Package: cnv.methyl
Title: cnv.methyl finds copy number alteration from methylation idat files
Year: 2022
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Izar", "de Villasante", "Llaquet", "idevillasante@carrerasresearch.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7325-0631 "))
Description: The package implements an automatic and dynamic thresholding algorithm to find somatic copy number alterations in methylation arrays based on log2R intensities. It relies mostly on minfi for preprocessing and and conumee for segmentation. 
